com.polarion.alm.shared.api.model.space

Interface SpaceSelector<T>


  • public interface SpaceSelector<T>
    Interface for selecting the space using optional project id and space path. The selection is finished by using space(String) method and the selector object cannot be used anymore after that.
    Since:
    3.9.0

    • Method Summary
